so help me to get some sales

To help improve your ad performance and potentially increase sales, here are a few tips:
1. **Targeting**: Refine your audience targeting to reach the most relevant users. Consider using interest, demographics, and location-based targeting.
2. **Ad Scheduling**: Schedule your ads to run during peak hours when your target audience is most active.
3. **Ad Creativity**: Invest in visually compelling ad content that resonates with your audience. A/B test different creatives to see which performs best.
4. **Budget Optimization**: Ensure your daily budget is sufficient to gather meaningful data and make adjustments as needed.
5. **Performance Monitoring**: Regularly review your ad performance in the Reporting tab and make necessary optimizations.
For more detailed guidance, you can check out our article on [Ad Creative Best Practices and A/B Testing](https://help.newsbreak.com/hc/en-us/articles/20676690598029-Ad-Creative-Best-Practices-and-A-B-Testing). If you have any other questions or need further assistance, feel free to ask!

how can i claim promo of $500 credit?

To claim a $500 ad credit, your account must meet certain eligibility criteria. First, ensure your account has completed and passed business verification. Additionally, your account or campaign should have accumulated over $5,000 in spend. Once these conditions are met, you can establish a relationship with an Account Manager who can request the ad credit functionality to be enabled for you. If you need further assistance, feel free to reach out to our Ad Support team at adsupport@newsbreak.com.
